name: ⑇ Fashion_Babe ⑉
description:
I did this piece while talking with some friends on twitter. The idea came to me unconsciously while i was trying to distract myself from the "Santa Bárbara" party at the neighbor house. This fashion queer babe looks like if two friends of mine had a baby. Wich is really kinda weird, but well. Don't worry, I apologize to them. This character also gives me "Elton John" vibes.

Well, I think it's going to be a long, long time)
